      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm a designer working on a new streetwear line. i want to make sure it hits right with the urban aesthetic without it feeling like we're just making fun of the culture or something. can u describe what an \"authentic\" urban look actually is so i can get the vibes right for the collection?",
