      "content": "that makes sense. when u say \"grit\" and \"raw\" graphics, do u mean specific styles or colors that are more tied to certain neighborhoods or communities? like, if i'm looking to capture that real city energy, what are the specific visual cues or clothing items that people in those urban areas actually wear to represent their identity?",
