      "content": "i get the materials part, but help me with the \"who\" behind it. usually when people talk about this aesthetic, they're talking about specific groups—u know, like Black or Latino communities in the inner city. if i'm designing this, should i be leaning into those specific ethnic styles or certain ways those groups dress to make it look real? or is it more universal than that?",
